INSERT INTO `quest_offer_reward` (`ID`, `Emote1`, `Emote2`, `Emote3`, `Emote4`, `EmoteDelay1`, `EmoteDelay2`, `EmoteDelay3`, `EmoteDelay4`, `RewardText`, `VerifiedBuild`) VALUES
(47738, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Rastakhan smiles grimly at you.>\n\nYou look like you have seen a loa. I know de feeling. Rezan will have words for me when I see him again.', 28153), -- -0-
(51677, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Jol wheezes.>\n\nThat did not... work how I imagined it would.', 28153), -- -0-
(47735, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'They are satisfactory. I will explain in due time what they are for.', 28153), -- -0-
(47733, 1, 14, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Dat snake of a womon helped Zul find de king! It is good dat she is dead, but I would have liked to kill her myself.\n\n<Zolani spits.>\n\nBwonsamdi can keep her.', 28153), -- -0-
(47739, 273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'De scent of blood is a reliable way to wake a devilsaur. De blood of traitorous wretches, even moreso.', 28153), -- -0-
(50235, 274, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I will try to help dem secure their village.\n\nStay sharp, $n. Zul will not stop while ol\' Rastakhan\'s fate hangs in de balance.', 28153), -- -0-
(51680, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Now you understand the precariousness of this situation. We will need your hands if we are to succeed in this complex bit of mending ahead of us.', 28153), -- -0-
(51101, 273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'It is good dat you have come. De king is dying, and we do not have much time to change dat.', 28153), -- -0-
(47528, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Shadra was... consumed? I have heard of such heresies in Zul\'Drak, but to hear of it in Zuldazar...', 28153), -- -0-
(47522, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'They seek to kill us. They seek to break us.$b$bAll they have done is unite us in what will be the greatest hunt the Zandalari have ever known.', 28153), -- -0-
(47963, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Heretics and ingrates! All of them! I will drop every last one of them on a ROCK!\n\nGo, little $r, and make sure the other loa are not falling into the same trap I did.', 28153), -- -0-
(47521, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'From here we can strike back at our enemies.', 28153), -- -0-
(47518, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Aya... did you have to bring Loti? She is never going to let me forget about dis.', 28153), -- -0-
(47520, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well done. Dat should blind Yazma.', 28153), -- -0-
(47915, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Free at last! Oh, de pain is coming for dem now.', 28153), -- -0-
(47897, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You killed how many? Well, dat is a start.', 28153), -- -0-
(47509, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '$p, glad to see you are not dead yet.', 28153), -- -0-
(49310, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'We are betrayed.', 28153), -- -0-
(49309, 6, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'De king is in danger!', 28153), -- -0-
(49149, 153, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Can you feel it? De spirits are flowing through you, and dey are pleased.', 28153), -- -0-
(49148, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Dey will reinforce their lines if we do not act soon. Dis may be our only opportunity.', 28153), -- -0-
(49147, 669, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Dey deserve worse fates, I assure you.', 28153), -- -0-
(49145, 396, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Our warriors won\'t soon forget you risking your own life to save theirs. Thank you.', 28153), -- -0-
(49144, 113, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You fight well, but our work is far from over.', 28153), -- -0-
(49146, 396, 11, 0, 0, 0, 300, 0, 0, 'You have done well. My friends on de Other Side are pleased.$B$BNow for de fun part.', 28153), -- -0-
(49122, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Things are worse than we thought.$B$BMuch worse.', 28153), -- -0-
(47432, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'So, you have chosen de path of Pa\'ku. May de winds of war be ever in your favor.$b$bFor myself, I follow Rezan, de devilsaur loa of kings. He and I have not spoken for many years, though.$b$bPerhaps I shall pay him a visit one of dese days.', 28153), -- -0-
(47440, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oh, good. She did not have you dropped. Dat is a good sign. Come, let us show de public your choice.', 28153), -- -0-
(47438, 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Your choice is made.', 28153), -- -0-
(47422, 661, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I will not have dat blood in my temple!', 28153), -- -0-
(47437, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Dis is worse than we thought.', 28153), -- -0-
(47434, 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Why are you scaring away my flock?', 28153), -- -0-
(47435, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Did you have to kill so many?', 28153), -- -0-
(47433, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Oh, so dat bent-tusk nose-breather is trying to win you over with a little flight and some charm, eh?', 28153), -- -0-
(47423, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'What? Dat sneering, vile raptor zealot is calling me out for not doing my share? Bah!', 28153), -- -0-
(49040, 18, 1, 0, 0, 0, 2000, 0, 0, '<B\'wizati reads the note and wipes a tear from her eye.>\n\nHe may choose to forget, but I choose to remember, no matter what pain it brings me. \n\nAt least he is safe. Loa watch over him.', 28153), -- -0-
(47445, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Welcome to de steps of Zanchul, $p. You will be treading on sacred ground soon.', 28153), -- -0-
(50881, 66, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Hmm. Zolani speaks highly of your deeds. Perhaps we may not need to kill you yet.', 28153), -- -0-
(46929, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'When visitors do not understand de language of your laws, it becomes necessary to explain your laws in a language dey do understand.', 28153), -- -0-
(46928, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ha ha ha. You can tell a lot about a tribe by what dey worship.', 28153), -- -0-
(46927, 11, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'It will not be long before these disciples are replaced with new ones. Hopefully, de next ones will learn from de past.', 28153), -- -0-
(46846, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, you are a competent errand-$r after all. Perhaps you could be trusted with more important tasks. Like trash removal.', 28153), -- -0-
(48454, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Blood magic being practiced in open daylight? Dis cannot stand.$b$bYou have done well in bringing me dis information. I will present it to King Rastakhan at de first opportunity when his council is away.', 28153), -- -0-
(46926, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You have my thanks. I think having someone of de Horde dispense dis justice was extra fitting.$b$bDe fact dat we have left our harbor so unprotected worries me greatly.', 28153), -- -0-
(48452, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Blood magic is an infection. It spreads like a disease if not purged.', 28153), -- -0-
(50835, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Let us get to work.', 28153), -- -0-
(49663, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Perhaps Zul will remember his place going forward.', 28153), -- -0-
(49905, 273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Death is a tool, $n. Do not forget dat.', 28153), -- -0-
(49495, 273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Zul rubs his hands together.>\n\nGood. Now we are ready to draw him out.', 28153), -- -0-
(51663, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good. I did not need to tell you to do dis thing.\n\nDe Jambani prepare for de fall of Zuldazar as foretold by Vol\'jamba. Dis will not happen, but destroying their stockpiles will make dem easier to eradicate once Rastakhan decides to deal with dis situation.', 28153), -- -0-
(49494, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Good. Dis thread has been severed.', 28153), -- -0-
(49493, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Weakness or pride... I think often on de Zandalari\'s priorities.', 28153); -- -0-
